	KEY:Exploitive Maneuver ~ Opp
	CATEGORY:Special Ability
	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary
	DESC:You use your enemy's actions in combat for your own gain, as if the opponent were using aid another to assist you, giving you a bonus on her next skill check, attack roll, or to AC against the next attack.
