	BENEFIT:You use your enemy's actions in combat for your own gain, as if the opponent were using aid another to assist you, giving you a bonus on her next skill check, attack roll, or to AC against the next attack. The enemy must be able to reach you, and you must activate this ability as an immediate action and succeed at a combat maneuver check against the enemy's CMD.

